<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلَا يَنْفُذُ حُكْمُهُ عَلَى:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- عَدُوِّهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَلَا لِنَفْسِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَلَا لِمَنْ لَا تُقْبَلُ شَهَادَتُهُ لَهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَنِ اسْتَعْدَاهُ عَلَى خَصْمٍ فِي البَلَدِ بِمَا تَتْبَعُهُ الهِمَّةُ:</span> لَزِمَهُ إِحْضَارُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- إِلَّا غَيْرَ بَرْزَةٍ، فَتُوَكِّلُ؛ كَمَرِيضٍ وَنَحْوِهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَإِنْ وَجَبَتْ <span class="c2">(١)</span> يَمِينٌ: أَرْسَلَ مَنْ يُحَلِّفُهُمَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَشُرِطَ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> كَوْنُ مُدَّعٍ وَمُنْكِرٍ جَائِزَيِ التَّصَرُّفِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَتَحْرِيرُ الدَّعْوَى.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَعِلْمُ مُدَّعًى بِهِ، إِلَّا فِيمَا نُصَحِّحُهُ مَجْهُولاً؛ كَوَصِيَّةٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَإِنِ ادَّعَى:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span class="c5"> عَقْداً:</span> ذَكَرَ شُرُوطَهُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (أ) و (ج): وجب.</p> </div>